<doc id="6979" wikidata="Q1254166" url="?curid=6979" title="Cell Cycle">
<text>Cell Cycle is a biweekly peer-reviewed scientific journal covering all aspects of cell biology. It was established in 2002. Originally published bimonthly, it is now published biweekly.

==Abstracting and indexing==
The journal is abstracted and indexed in:

According to the &quot;Journal Citation Reports&quot;, the journal has a 5-year impact factor of 7.7.
==See also==
* &quot;Autophagy&quot;
* &quot;Cell Biology International&quot;
* &quot;Cell and Tissue Research&quot;

